llar.\n\nKnow what your wine is worth. Check live market value on any bottle and compare it against your own selling price — right from your phone.\n\nSee what's working. Track cellar value, consumption, corked bottles, top movers and much more.\n\nTaste and score. Rate wines, keep tasting notes, and share organized tasting sessions with your team and friends.\n\nConnect your POS. Vinify integrates with your point-of-sale so sales update inventory automatically — contact our team and we'll set it up for you.\n\nWhether you're running 1,000 bottles in your personal cellar or 20,000 across a hotel group, Vinify scales with you.\n\nTrusted by top wine programs across the USA, Europe and Asia.\n\nEven more pro features are available on the web version on your computer, on vinify.app.","averageUserRating":3.90698,"sellerUrl":"http://blog.vinify.app/download","languageCodesISO2A":["EN","NB"],"fileSizeBytes":"99681280","formattedPrice":"Free","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":86,"trackContentRating":"17+","averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":3.90698,"trackCensoredName":"Vinify: Wine Cellar Manager","trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/vinify-wine-cellar-manager/id1449167552?uo=4","contentAdvisoryRating":"17+","minimumOsVersion":"17.0","sellerName":"Vinify AS","trackName":"Vinify: Wine Cellar Manager","trackId":1449167552,"primaryGenreName":"Food & Drink","primaryGenreId":6023,"genreIds":["6023"],"userRatingCount":86}